comment: Grant's (PHI) contact does not affect Williams' (CHA) RSBQ.
Williams (CHA) is outside the restricted area and establishes himself in Grant's (PHI) path before the contact.
Aldemir (PHI) sets the screen on Henderson (CHA) and gives him the opportunity to stop and/or change direction.
Williams (CHA) falls to the floor with the ball but does not move while on the floor.
Williams (CHA) commits a take foul on Smith (PHI).
Aldemir (PHI) jumps vertically and remains vertical at the time of the contact with Henderson (CHA).
Taylor (CHA) dislodges Aldemir (PHI) and prevents him from retrieving the rebound.
